speaker.name: Susan Boland
speaker.speakerTitle: Associate Director of Public and Research Services
speaker.bio: I joined the law library as the Associate Director of Public and Research Services last year. I teach legal research and offer reference and research support services to all law library users. Prior to joining the law library faculty, I was the Head of Information Services at Indiana University School of Law -- Indianapolis, Research & Instructional Services librarian at Northern Illinois University College of Law, and a judicial clerk for the State of Iowa.
